Format on populated runs:

```
### <screen-name>

- [ ] **[abc1234567]** <ruleId> / <severity> / <viewport> — <message>
  - **Element:** `<selector>`
  - **Status:** pending | fixed-in-place | deferred | dismissed
  - **Notes:** (—)
```

Status values:
- `pending` — newly detected, awaiting triage
- `fixed-in-place` — author confirms the underlying issue is resolved (next run verifies)
- `deferred` — moves to "Triage Backlog" section; revisit later
- `dismissed` — false positive or intentional; reason documented in Notes

